uriemann(false)$
for a thru dim do for b thru dim do
  for c thru (if symmetricp(lg,dim) then b else dim) do
    for d thru (if symmetricp(lg,dim) then a else dim) do
      if lriem[a,b,c,d]≠0 then
        ishow('R([],[ξ[d],ξ[a],ξ[b],ξ[c]])=uriem[a,b,c,d])$
